sql:
SELECT c.name, c.symbol
FROM cryptocurrencies c
JOIN crypto_exchange_bridge cb ON c.crypto_id = cb.crypto_id
WHERE cb.exchange_id = (
    SELECT exchange_id FROM exchanges WHERE name = 'Binance'
);

SELECT c.name, c.symbol, c.website, c.social_media
FROM cryptocurrencies c
JOIN article_crypto_bridge acb ON c.crypto_id = acb.crypto_id;

external_knowledge:
Binance is one of the largest cryptocurrency exchanges; 
The query focuses on market data for cryptocurrencies, specifically their trading volumes (values) on this exchange; 
Average market value for each cryptocurrency is calculated by considering all market data entries for that cryptocurrency on Binance.

